{
  "stem": "2522.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By this time I'm at MIT, and somebody tells me, you know, there's this peculiar machine in the laboratory called a computer, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that could sort of analyze these cards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To make the story short, I wrote the first dissertation in the United States on business applications of computers, which is still considered to be somewhat of a classical, 'The Scheduling of Toll Collection Personnel on the New Jersey Turnpike.' Got paid royally for that thing.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Got paid royally for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Could afford getting married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I was drawing $4,000 a year, by that time, going to school, graduate school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Paid for tuition, got married, could afford $35 a month rent in Marine barracks from-- left from Second World War.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, pig's heaven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And got into computers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The year was 1954?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And stayed in computers ever since.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's a great-- great story, a great tidal wave that took you through a remarkable career.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and you-- you spent part of your career in recent years doing work for the US government.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well that-- you know, you always find these philosophical explanations after the fact.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I think people are what they are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have certain beliefs, a certain consistency.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it's amazing that I meet my peer group who are my age now, in Israel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In-- in terms of character and attitude, they fundamentally are still the same as they were 50 years ago when I knew them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm basically a creature of my environment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and after being successful in business and being vice president and chief computer executive and a rather prominent member of the computer fraternity, held a number of very significant posts.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
